		<h2 align="left"><a name="feeding"></a>Caring for Your Puffle - Feeding</h2>
		<div align="right">
          <table width="100%" height="256"  border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td height="256" valign="top"><ul>
                  <li>
                    <p align="left" class="plaintext"> Buy your puffle food by clicking the third button from the left at the bottom of the puffle player card. You can choose to feed it Puffle-0&rsquo;s for healthy snack, a cookie or bubble gum for a yummy treat. Depending on its level of health it may even do a trick!  </p>
                    <ul><li>
                        <div align="left"><a href="#feeding">Feeding</a></div>
                      </li>
