		<h2 align="left"><a name="bath" ></a>Caring for Your Puffle - Bathing</h2>
		<div align="right">
          <table width="100%" height="256"  border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td height="256" valign="top"><ul>
                  <li>
                    <p align="left" class="plaintext">To bath your puffle, click on it and pull up its player card.  Click the food icon located along the bottom menu. The food icon will open a tab with different options for feeding your puffle. Choose the water bowl icon on the second row and watch how your puffle plays in water. It will cost 5 coins each time.                    </p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        <div align="left"><a href="#feeding">Feeding</a></div>
                      </li>
