        <h2 align="left"><a name="playing"></a>Caring for Your Puffle - Playing </h2>
        <div align="right">
          <table width="100%" height="258"  border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td height="258" valign="top"><ul>
                  <li>
                    <p align="left" class="plaintext"> Puffles love to play and it keeps them healthy. To play with your puffle, click on the far left button at the bottom of the puffle player card. When it is really healthy it may surprise you and change its type of activity.                    </p>
                    <ul><li>
                        <div align="left"><a href="#feeding">Feeding</a></div>
                      </li>
					  <li>
                        <div align="left"><a href="#bath">Bathing</a></div>
