		<h2 align="left"><a name="Puffle_Furniture"></a>Puffle Furniture</h2>
		<table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" height="242" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><div align="left">To buy furniture for your puffle, go to the pet shop (located in the Plaza).
                        <ul>
                            <li>Click on the yellow catalog</li>
                            <li>Click the &ldquo;Buy&rdquo; button for the item you want to buy. </li>
                        </ul>
                      The red catalog allows you to adopt a puffle. </div></td>
                </tr>
